summary:
My goal is to be the best in the Industry. To motivate and inspire others. To create innovative tools and processes to make international mobility a less complex and difficult process for our clients. 

I have worked, lived and studied in seven different countries. I have learned and grown from these international assignments. Living and working with a Diversity of Cultures has become my work but also my lifestyle.

I love what I do, and it shows!

Specialties: International Immigration Law
Fully accredited EURA Level III member
